text: Best Wanton in chilli oil tried as a foodie! I am back the second time to the totally revamped Hawker Street, at Bukit Panjang Plaza, to try this dish again, with the Dan Dan noodles too. It is so peanutty and flavorsome i just can't shake off the fantastic taste still in my mind!

$5.90 for the zhajiangmian.  It's good but the serving is toooo small, it would leave you still hungry.  I've ate here few times to check incase if its just my unlucky day, but really that's the serving.  I feel like it doesn't justify the price
This is super tasty! The skin is soft and the fillings comes with delicious soup and tender pork. Very nice!

The noodles were delicious‚Äîflavorful and well-cooked! The xiao long bao was also amazing, with juicy fillings. üòã

However, the food court seating is very limited, making it hard to find a spot during peak hours. If not for the crowded space, it would be a perfect meal!
